A video of a man engulfed in flames has gone viral on social media. The fire was reportedly caused by a cellphone the man had in his pocket.
The incident was initially believed to have happened in Dubai, yet Diamantine, a clothing store, is located in Casablanca, Morocco.
In the video, the man can be seen wandering through the mall in flames, with people trying to put the fire out with their clothes. Screams and panic can be seen as the man frantically takes his pants off inside the mall.

