Dubai police have called the video fake after the incident was reported to have happened in a mall in Dubai, according to Gulf News.
The police pointed out the incident happened in Morocco on Sunday, June 3.
Another report, however, paints the man on fire as a “would-be shoplifter”. The report by Morocco World News claims the man was a shoplifter who set himself on fire at the Agadir supermarket.